column5: A group of us leave this evening for Red Lake. Fly out 5 am Saturday morning and really looking forward to it. just seeing when everyone else is leaving and where they are going. have a good one guys
I LEAVE TONIGHT FOR NUNGESSER LAKE. ITS 40MILES NORTH OF RED LAKE. WHAT LAKE ARE YOU GOING TO?
going to Birch Lake. greens flyin service

Hey Iowa guy, Email me. We have been going with Green's to Birch for many years, but will miss this year and go to Savant a couple times instead. I've got the DT's over not going to Birch this year............ I don't think Reg is going to be there the last I heard. Odds are I've met you or your group. Iowa City area? Pooch in central Illinois[email protected]
